@node Connecting Claude
@chapter Connecting Claude
@cindex Claude
@cindex Anthropic
@cindex Claude Desktop
@cindex Claude Code

This chapter covers wiring OwnSona to Anthropic's products: Claude
Desktop, Claude Code, and the Anthropic Messages API.  Once the
connection is in place, every Claude conversation has access to your
durable memory through the @code{remember}/@code{recall}/@code{forget}
tools.

